{"tid":949953,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿包裹多次被偷 NASA工程師設臭氣陷阱騙竊賊","createTime":"2018-12-21T07:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T18:59:07.000Z","uid":49391,"like":445,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc73274f99bade1221d49ab8141ed4f3a9f189c","tid":949953,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xoxhDk-hwuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxoxhDk-hwuo&d=fIRXLna9qUL1bxMY6drnYSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5dec5f23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xoxhDk-hwuo</a><br />\n美國前NASA工程師為懲治偷他包裹的竊賊，自製一個會噴七彩亮粉和臭氣噴霧的假包裹，放在家門口誘使嫌犯順手牽羊，結果順利騙到幾位竊賊，還拍下他們嚇到的窘狀，讓網友看了直呼大快人心。<br />\n<br />\n前NASA工程師馬克‧羅伯（Mark Rober）今年5月發現，偶爾會收不到上網訂購的商品，調閱監視器才發現，是有小偷將郵差放在家門口的包裹拿走了，為了教訓竊賊，他決定發揮專長製作假包裹。<br />\n<br />\n羅伯找來一款蘋果產品的空盒，在裡面安裝七彩亮粉噴罐、臭氣噴霧，還裝了四台智慧型手機，打算拍下竊賊的長相，並透過GPS追蹤所在位置，透過簡訊將地址傳給羅伯，竊賊一旦打開包裹，所有機關便會同時啟動。<br />\n<br />\n從羅伯公開的影片中可見，有的竊賊偷了包裹後，上車便興沖沖地拆開包裝，也有的竊賊回到家才打開，不過最後的下場都是把車內或房間搞得一團糟，身上還沾染臭氣，只好趕緊把包裹棄置。<br />\n<br />\n羅伯在影片中表示，自從使用假包裹騙竊賊後，目前就再也沒有包裹被偷了，他呼籲大家不要亂拿不屬於自己的東西，並希望這場惡作劇能夠引起觀眾對科學和工程的興趣。羅伯還強調，假包裹是非賣品。<br />\n<br />\n羅伯的影片從17日推出至今已累積三千多萬人觀看，許多有相同經歷的網友紛紛留言直呼大快人心，甚至有網友認為光是臭氣和七彩亮粉還不足以懲罰竊賊，建議裝上高音喇叭或噴漆，甚至用倒數計時器假裝內有炸藥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/20/99/5685779.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F20%2F99%2F5685779.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=37dcba25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅伯在假包裹裡安裝七彩亮粉噴罐、臭氣噴霧，以及四台智慧型手機。 圖擷自YouTube<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3547269?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3547269%3Ffrom%3Dudn-referralnews_ch2artbottom&d=fIRXLna9qUL1bxMY6drnYSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d776a614\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3547269?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom</a>"},{"pid":"b625ce788f28ac3b4d366b0847b09676ecaf59fb","tid":949953,"uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"影視台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fbf9138ef4a40ed24be2093c826dda07947f08","tid":949953,"uid":49391,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"quote":{"pid":"b625ce788f28ac3b4d366b0847b09676ecaf59fb","tid":949953,"uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"影視台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"有Home Alone彩蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894b7a927f296f731bb2fb992ced121cb869fd7e","tid":949953,"uid":8636,"like":24,"dislike":162,"score":-138,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:00:08.000Z","msg":"嘩外國人咁高尚都咁多人偷野嘅"},{"pid":"2fae8546a125f14c60a9b9e069cbde723ac08959","tid":949953,"uid":201649,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"好抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0072daa8a2305e0cd43bfbbfb1a144d07dd2bcad","tid":949953,"uid":208581,"like":7,"dislike":317,"score":-310,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"如果拎咗包裹個人嚇到心撞病發，又或者係衝出馬路比車撞死咗，佢係咪犯法？"},{"pid":"9331ba694e527d990ef99ac2166c09f7b8567ef8","tid":949953,"uid":25100,"like":171,"dislike":3,"score":168,"quote":{"pid":"0072daa8a2305e0cd43bfbbfb1a144d07dd2bcad","tid":949953,"uid":208581,"like":7,"dislike":317,"score":-310,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"如果拎咗包裹個人嚇到心撞病發，又或者係衝出馬路比車撞死咗，佢係咪犯法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"大陸就會<br />\n仲要賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16806f2e87342a842aba70b0c16ba4710467c1b3","tid":949953,"uid":72749,"like":209,"dislike":11,"