id":949953,"uid":43850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0072daa8a2305e0cd43bfbbfb1a144d07dd2bcad","tid":949953,"uid":208581,"like":7,"dislike":317,"score":-310,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"如果拎咗包裹個人嚇到心撞病發，又或者係衝出馬路比車撞死咗，佢係咪犯法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"屌鳩你都廢事 直接ban<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af7a0e2a83c65ea7c34077699bd462245c54a7d","tid":949953,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"fcc73274f99bade1221d49ab8141ed4f3a9f189c","tid":949953,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xoxhDk-hwuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxoxhDk-hwuo&d=fIRXLna9qUL1bxMY6drnYSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5dec5f23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xoxhDk-hwuo</a><br />\n美國前NASA工程師為懲治偷他包裹的竊賊，自製一個會噴七彩亮粉和臭氣噴霧的假包裹，放在家門口誘使嫌犯順手牽羊，結果順利騙到幾位竊賊，還拍下他們嚇到的窘狀，讓網友看了直呼大快人心。<br />\n<br />\n前NASA工程師馬克‧羅伯（Mark Rober）今年5月發現，偶爾會收不到上網訂購的商品，調閱監視器才發現，是有小偷將郵差放在家門口的包裹拿走了，為了教訓竊賊，他決定發揮專長製作假包裹。<br />\n<br />\n羅伯找來一款蘋果產品的空盒，在裡面安裝七彩亮粉噴罐、臭氣噴霧，還裝了四台智慧型手機，打算拍下竊賊的長相，並透過GPS追蹤所在位置，透過簡訊將地址傳給羅伯，竊賊一旦打開包裹，所有機關便會同時啟動。<br />\n<br />\n從羅伯公開的影片中可見，有的竊賊偷了包裹後，上車便興沖沖地拆開包裝，也有的竊賊回到家才打開，不過最後的下場都是把車內或房間搞得一團糟，身上還沾染臭氣，只好趕緊把包裹棄置。<br />\n<br />\n羅伯在影片中表示，自從使用假包裹騙竊賊後，目前就再也沒有包裹被偷了，他呼籲大家不要亂拿不屬於自己的東西，並希望這場惡作劇能夠引起觀眾對科學和工程的興趣。羅伯還強調，假包裹是非賣品。<br />\n<br />\n羅伯的影片從17日推出至今已累積三千多萬人觀看，許多有相同經歷的網友紛紛留言直呼大快人心，甚至有網友認為光是臭氣和七彩亮粉還不足以懲罰竊賊，建議裝上高音喇叭或噴漆，甚至用倒數計時器假裝內有炸藥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/20/99/5685779.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F20%2F99%2F5685779.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=37dcba25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅伯在假包裹裡安裝七彩亮粉噴罐、臭氣噴霧，以及四台智慧型手機。 圖擷自YouTube<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3547269?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F3547269%3Ffrom%3Dudn-referralnews_ch2artbottom&d=fIRXLna9qUL1bxMY6drnYSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=d776a614\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/3547269?from=udn-referralnews_ch2artbottom</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bf0649afb59a263881eab36fd3ebbce6dbf7f8","tid":949953,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f391e5c9bcd01a2f2843c50b36ce9890e4d65c99","tid":949953,"uid":43718,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"玩都要咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"外國人係高質啲"},{"pid":"991065cb93741bbdb683efe725fe016cbab048a5","tid":949953,"uid":225828,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f391e5c9bcd01a2f2843c50b36ce9890e4d65c99","tid":949953,"uid":43718,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"玩都要咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T03:36:50.000Z","msg":"Work hard <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Play Hard<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"404959a47e9dd07965fc04b24f767eed142161cd","tid":949953,"uid":225828,"like":0